{"tid":859947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國將向巴基斯坦出售48架大型軍事級無人機","createTime":"2018-10-13T03:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T03:39:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a51185063a66fb03720e6da7ae52fa65f3537c","tid":859947,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"中國將向巴出售48架大型軍事級無人機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-china-to-sell-48-military-grade-drones-to-pakistan-20181010/4607412.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fnews-china-to-sell-48-military-grade-drones-to-pakistan-20181010%2F4607412.html&d=ebHhyDX2PSbaHo9MmOsjRP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=309ac38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-china-to-sell-48-military-grade-drones-to-pakistan-20181010/4607412.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中共喉舌環球時報星期二稱，巴基斯坦空軍披露，巴基斯坦決定向中國購買48架可用於偵察和打擊等多功能的 &ldquo;翼龍II&rdquo; 大型無人機，將以中巴合作生產的形式完成。一旦落實，這將是該無人機公開的第二大出口單，也是&ldquo;翼龍II&rdquo;生產線的首次公開出口。<br />\n<br />\n環時的報導表示，巴基斯坦空軍&ldquo;雄獅之心&rdquo;特技飛行表演隊10月6日在臉書賬號上發布，巴航空工業綜合體將與成都飛機工業公司共同生產48架&ldquo;翼龍II&rdquo;無人作戰飛機。<br />\n<br />\n儘管該消息沒有透露任何細節，但鑑於中巴兩國關係一向緊密，巴軍方已採購大量中國武器裝備，包括&ldquo;彩虹&rdquo;系列無人機，因此消息受到外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;翼龍II&rdquo; 是中國航空工業集團有製造的新一代集偵察打擊一體的軍事級無人機，續航能力達至少20小時，可攜掛多枚地對空導彈，去年2月首飛成功。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦2015年就公開了引進中國生產線生產的&ldquo;彩虹3&rdquo;無人機。而&ldquo;翼龍II&rdquo;無人機在續航、打擊能力及空間上，都遠超&ldquo;彩虹3&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"a30f0b294a83ba83c8ff068702289e962bf65adb","tid":859947,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到打仗時，解放軍發出指令控制呢堆無人機"},{"pid":"bdd574ce78ed9bd24f7dcefb1567cdbe890d4348","tid":859947,"uid":106810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"巴基岩先話無錢，又賒數？"},{"pid":"a5575bc5ec91e229879f214e8b865dd0203d871f","tid":859947,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbeeb4bbe32d1e49401e0981d6afd28231df9bfb","tid":859947,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"美帝啲科技就係俾蝗国咁樣用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5626a872b81b46071fc477c5ffc8595f5804928d","tid":859947,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"翼龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等絕種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c99df235eb11ed87662f739d871e91ee5c93559","tid":859947,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdd574ce78ed9bd24f7dcefb1567cdbe890d4348","tid":859947,"uid":106810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"巴基岩先話無錢，又賒數？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"IMF 唔好俾錢佢<br />\n巴基原來用黎買武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}